RTBFAuvio.aPodcast.description: Used with general string "Listening to" to form "Listening to a Podcast" in privacy mode

RTBFAuvio.aRadio.description: Used with general string "Listening to" to form "Listening to a Radio" in privacy mode.

RTBFAuvio.buttonViewCategory.description: Used as the title for the button in Discord

RTBFAuvio.deferred.description: Used when a livestream is no longer live but with a delay. Often because the content has been paused or rewound.

RTBFAuvio.endsIn.description: Used when a livestream is about to end. {0} is used to write the time before end.

RTBFAuvio.liveEnded.description: Used when a livestream is over

RTBFAuvio.on.description: Used to specify that content is on a channel or by default on Auvio. For example "Iron Man on Auvio"

RTBFAuvio.privatePlay.description: Used when playing in privacy mode

RTBFAuvio.startsIn.description: Used when a livestream is about to be launched. {0} is used to write the time before launch.

RTBFAuvio.toAPodcast.description: Used with ActivityType "Listening" to form "Listening to a Podcast" in privacy mode

RTBFAuvio.toARadio.description: Used with ActivityType "Listening" to form "Listening to a Radio" in privacy mode.
